'''{{Colour|red|Warning}}:''' Spindel resides in level 29 [[Wilderness]]. You may be attacked by other players at any time during the fight. '''Do not''' bring any items that you are not willing to lose. Items like the [[dragon defender]] are '''permanently''' lost if not protected beyond level 20 Wilderness. 

Spindel is a level 302 [[spider]] [[boss]] that is found in the [[Web Chasm]]. The fight with her is nearly identical to [[Venenatis]], although with reduced stats and in a [[singles-plus combat]] area. Completion of the hard [[Wilderness Diary|Wilderness diary]] is required to fight Spindel. 

==Transportation==
Spindel is located in the [[Web Chasm]], which is a lair located in the ruins north of the [[Graveyard of Shadows]] in level 29 [[Wilderness]].

* [[Carrallanger teleport (tablet)|Graveyard of Shadows teleport]], then run north.
* Teleport to [[Ferox Enclave]] and run north past [[Green dragon|green dragons]], or head north-east around the graveyard.
* Teleport to the level 26 [[Revenant Caves]] entrance with a [[revenant cave teleport]] and run east.
* With the [[Hunter cape]], teleport to the [[Black chinchompa (Hunter)|black chinchompas]] and run south east. The hunter cape will be lost if the player dies in level 30 or higher wilderness.
* Take a [[canoe]] to the wilderness pond and run south east.
* A [[games necklace]] to teleport to the [[Corporeal Beast's Lair|Corporeal Beast's lair]], exit the cave then run north-west.

==Attacks==
Spindel has many attacks that she uses against her target. 

*Melee attack: She simply lunges at the player. This is the only normal attack she will use if the player is within melee distance.
*Ranged attack: Launches green spit at players.
*Magic attack: Launches webs at players.
*Sticky Web: Spindel will occasionally deploy a sticky web at a player, sending a white-blue web at the target's location. It will then expand into a 7x5 AoE - while in this web, any player caught in it will take rapid hits of 3 damage, have their prayer drained by 3, and run energy by 10.
**Note that [[aranea boots]] will only negate the first tick of damage taken from the web attack.
*Spiderlings: Spindel will occasionally call some [[Spindel's Spiderling|spiderlings]] to assist her in battle. While fairly weak, they will drain prayer on every hit regardless if prayed against or hits. They will also increase her damage and allow her to hit through prayers if left alive. Thrall damage is reduced while spiderlings are alive.

