Ranged=
Both the [[webweaver bow]] and [[Craw's bow]] offer very competitive damage against Spindel despite her higher ranged defences. Ranged also has the luxury of staying closer to the exit in case of [[player killers]], although you will need to monitor and change your overhead prayers depending on the attack cycle. The [[twisted bow]] and [[bow of Faerdhinen]] are also both strong alternatives to some melee setups. Crossbows generally perform worse than most melee weapons.
